.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:666:"<p>Let&#8217;s keep this brief. Pligg 2.0 is now available in beta form <a href="http://pligg.com/downloads/package/pligg-cms/">via the Pligg Pro shop</a>. Starting at $5 you can get early access to the next version of Pligg. For larger donation amounts we are including several popular modules at a big discount.</p>
